ZH: 毛孔是我们皮肤的一部分。
EN: Pores are a part of our skin.

ZH: 要保持毛孔清洁很重要。
EN: It is important to keep pores clean.

ZH: 有些人的毛孔会被污垢堵塞。
EN: Some people's pores can get clogged with dirt.

ZH: 毛孔可以通过清洁来缩小。
EN: Pores can be minimized through cleansing.

ZH: 毛孔会因为挤压而变得更大。
EN: Pores can become larger due to squeezing.

ZH: 毛孔会随着年龄增长而变得更加显眼。
EN: Pores can become more prominent as we age.

ZH: 痤疮可以影响毛孔的健康。
EN: Acne can affect the health of pores.

ZH: 通过磨砂可以减少毛孔的粗糙程度。
EN: Exfoliation can reduce the roughness of pores.

ZH: 水分可以帮助调节毛孔的大小。
EN: Hydration can help regulate the size of pores.

ZH: 太阳暴晒可以引起毛孔扩大。
EN: Sun exposure can cause pores to enlarge.

ZH: 营养不良可能导致毛孔变得粗糙。
EN: Poor nutrition can lead to rough pores.

ZH: 毛孔会因为过度油脂分泌而被堵塞。
EN: Pores can get blocked due to excessive sebum production.

ZH: 粉刺可以影响毛孔的清洁度。
EN: Blackheads can affect the cleanliness of pores.

ZH: 毛孔处于生长周期中会有更多的脂质分泌。
EN: Pores produce more sebum during their growth cycle.

ZH: 毛孔可以被污垢和化妆品堵塞。
EN: Pores can get blocked by dirt and makeup.

ZH: 高强度的运动可以帮助毛孔排出污垢。
EN: Intense exercise can help pores expel dirt.

ZH: 毛孔的通透程度会受到环境的影响。
EN: The clarity of pores can be affected by the environment.

ZH: 紧张情绪会导致毛孔变大。
EN: Stress can cause pores to enlarge.

ZH: 某些化妆品可能会堵塞毛孔。
EN: Certain cosmetics may clog pores.

ZH: 用温水清洁可以打开毛孔。
